        {
            "title": "〈台幣〉貶勢收斂驚險守住32元 3月來狂貶6.67角",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DrnTtrTMIahxF00oJj6HIw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/cnyes_hk_559/a8176f064e0350ee5922e722b4d80b55\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
